WEBVTT

00:20.360 --> 00:22.120
Bravo!

00:23.720 --> 00:26.200
Wonderful!

00:26.280 --> 00:31.240
XIANGTENG TROUPE

01:00.400 --> 01:02.120
Stop running!

01:02.200 --> 01:04.000
Hey!

01:06.000 --> 01:06.880
I'll handle it.

01:10.040 --> 01:11.000
Bravo!

01:16.480 --> 01:18.360
‎Sooie! Sooie!

01:31.720 --> 01:33.200
That's it?

01:42.200 --> 01:43.480
Done already?

01:43.560 --> 01:44.720
That girl's something else.

01:45.720 --> 01:47.000
Be a good pig in this life.

01:47.080 --> 01:48.040
Be a good person in the next.

02:01.040 --> 02:03.880
It's done. The blood's filling up.
Bring another basin.

03:39.520 --> 03:44.600
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

03:49.400 --> 03:51.360
We'll be opening the feast soon.

03:51.440 --> 03:52.600
-All right.
-Sounds good.

03:52.680 --> 03:53.520
No rush.

03:57.520 --> 03:59.520
Didn't the Fan family
just finish mourning?

03:59.600 --> 04:01.160
So why's Mrs. Chen

04:01.240 --> 04:02.960
invited Changyu to slaughter
the New Year pig?

04:04.320 --> 04:06.240
Out of pity, that's why.

04:06.320 --> 04:08.680
Her parents were killed by bandits.

04:08.760 --> 04:10.000
Left nothing behind

04:10.080 --> 04:11.960
but two girls.

04:12.640 --> 04:15.040
Thank heavens Changyu's capable.

04:15.720 --> 04:17.240
She followed her father's trade.

04:17.320 --> 04:19.079
Slaughtering pigs to keep the family fed.

04:19.160 --> 04:21.160
She's the one
holding the Fan household up.

04:21.880 --> 04:23.040
Poor child.

04:23.120 --> 04:25.200
The Fans were such decent people.

04:25.280 --> 04:26.880
How did fate turn on them like this?

04:26.960 --> 04:28.520
-Kang.
-Come, come, sit.

04:28.600 --> 04:30.040
It's that girl. She brings misfortune.

04:31.120 --> 04:33.600
-Don't talk nonsense.
-Didn't I say it before?

04:34.520 --> 04:36.720
Mrs. Fan was far too pretty.

04:36.800 --> 04:37.960
Who's to say

04:38.040 --> 04:39.440
she didn't come from a pleasure house?

04:39.520 --> 04:41.920
Otherwise, how would she
marry a pig butcher?

04:47.800 --> 04:49.280
Heavens above.

04:49.360 --> 04:50.720
The dead should be respected.

04:50.800 --> 04:51.640
Let it rest.

04:52.240 --> 04:53.560
Am I wrong?

04:54.400 --> 04:57.880
She may have her mother's delicate looks,

04:57.960 --> 05:00.000
but that strength of hers…

05:00.080 --> 05:01.280
Not to mention a girl.

05:01.360 --> 05:03.640
Even a grown man couldn't match it.

05:06.160 --> 05:07.120
Look at her.

05:08.200 --> 05:09.040
That girl's fate

05:09.120 --> 05:10.440
is too hard.

05:10.520 --> 05:11.920
And that's not just me saying so.

05:12.000 --> 05:14.080
Wasn't she betrothed to Song Yan?

05:14.160 --> 05:16.720
The Song family
went to match their birth charts.

05:17.360 --> 05:19.040
The results?

05:19.120 --> 05:20.640
Not good.

05:20.720 --> 05:22.760
A calamity star. Destined to be alone.

05:22.840 --> 05:24.520
I never heard that.

05:24.600 --> 05:26.120
The Song family broke off the engagement

05:26.200 --> 05:27.960
-at once.
-So that's what happened.

05:29.000 --> 05:29.840
What are you doing?

05:29.920 --> 05:33.280
Kang, some pig's blood water for you.
Wash away the ill fortune.

05:33.360 --> 05:34.960
-Hey…
-What…

05:35.680 --> 05:37.040
Look at her! No manners at all!

05:38.800 --> 05:40.920
-What a mess.
-Mrs. Chen said

05:41.000 --> 05:43.320
half this New Year pig
goes to the neighbors.

05:43.400 --> 05:44.360
Come choose your share.

05:45.880 --> 05:46.760
Hey, you…

05:47.480 --> 05:49.440
-Let's go.
-Come on.

05:49.520 --> 05:50.560
Hey!

05:50.640 --> 05:52.600
What did I say that was wrong?

05:52.680 --> 05:54.800
You… You're a jinx!

05:54.880 --> 05:56.200
You brought death to your parents.

05:56.280 --> 05:57.440
-Drove off your betrothed.
-Enough.

05:57.520 --> 05:59.600
Your sister's been sickly since birth.

05:59.680 --> 06:01.520
-That's your curse too.
-That's enough!

06:01.600 --> 06:02.480
Look at her…

06:02.560 --> 06:03.960
Don't miss your share, Kang.

06:04.680 --> 06:05.960
Wait!

06:06.040 --> 06:07.840
Don't grab. This piece is mine!

06:07.920 --> 06:09.400
This piece is mine.

06:09.480 --> 06:11.800
I was here first!

06:26.360 --> 06:27.520
Changyu.

06:27.600 --> 06:29.080
Here's your slaughter fee for today.

06:29.800 --> 06:30.640
Thank you, Mrs. Chen.

06:30.720 --> 06:31.960
We're about to start the banquet.

06:32.040 --> 06:33.000
Stay and eat with us.

06:33.760 --> 06:34.840
I'll pass.

06:34.920 --> 06:37.040
We've just finished mourning at home.

06:37.560 --> 06:40.200
The fact you still asked me to come

06:40.280 --> 06:41.320
means more than enough.

06:42.560 --> 06:43.400
All right then.

06:43.920 --> 06:46.040
Take these offal cuts.

06:46.120 --> 06:47.120
I can't possibly…

06:47.800 --> 06:48.840
Take them.

06:49.600 --> 06:51.560
Your father used to make
the finest braised meats.

06:52.200 --> 06:54.880
If anyone should have this, it's you.

06:54.960 --> 06:56.240
Cook it for Ning.

07:00.600 --> 07:01.440
Thank you.

07:02.160 --> 07:03.480
I'll head back now.

07:03.560 --> 07:05.200
Ning's waiting at home.

07:08.360 --> 07:09.280
Changyu!

07:10.240 --> 07:12.520
There's fighting in Chongzhou.
It's unsettled around here too.

07:13.360 --> 07:15.360
Be careful on the road.

07:15.440 --> 07:16.800
Don't worry.

07:16.880 --> 07:19.480
I checked the almanac before I left.
It's a lucky day.

07:26.520 --> 07:27.840
Such a good girl.

07:28.880 --> 07:31.600
Just born under a bitter fate.

07:37.480 --> 07:40.040
Four, five, six…

07:40.120 --> 07:44.400
Ten, 11, 12, 14…

08:28.360 --> 08:29.360
Forgive me.

08:30.680 --> 08:33.200
Forgive me. Please.

08:34.480 --> 08:36.480
I'm sorry. I didn't see you.

08:37.000 --> 08:38.280
Be a good pig in this life.

08:38.360 --> 08:39.320
Be a good person in the next.

08:39.400 --> 08:40.480
I truly didn't mean it.

08:41.080 --> 08:42.720
Jade Emperor, Queen Mother…

09:03.960 --> 09:04.800
Not breathing.

09:07.320 --> 09:09.200
He's… He's barely breathing.

09:11.360 --> 09:12.480
Changyu.

09:12.560 --> 09:13.520
Go home.

09:18.320 --> 09:20.440
I can't afford to save him.
There's no money in this house.

09:20.520 --> 09:22.840
And I still have my sister.
What if he's a bad guy?

09:23.520 --> 09:24.640
Changyu, don't go soft.

09:24.720 --> 09:25.880
Go home. Go home.

09:25.960 --> 09:27.720
Go home. Go home…

09:28.280 --> 09:30.000
I'll save you!

09:33.160 --> 09:34.160
You can't die.

09:34.760 --> 09:35.720
Please don't die.

09:37.640 --> 09:38.600
It's all right.

09:44.080 --> 09:46.120
Be a good pig in this life.
Be a good person in the next.

09:58.920 --> 10:01.280
Go back and find…

10:02.080 --> 10:03.120
Mother…

10:12.320 --> 10:14.200
It must be Mother guiding me to you.

10:18.400 --> 10:19.240
Stay with me.

10:20.000 --> 10:20.920
You mustn't die.

10:22.000 --> 10:23.120
My mother wants me to save you.

10:44.160 --> 10:45.000
Ning!

10:47.240 --> 10:49.000
-Open the door, Ning!
-Changyu.

10:50.000 --> 10:52.040
I went into town today
to see a shadow play.

10:52.120 --> 10:53.760
It was about a woman general!

10:55.280 --> 10:56.880
-Changyu?
-Grab my stuff.

11:05.360 --> 11:06.280
Changyu!

11:07.520 --> 11:08.360
Who is this?

11:08.440 --> 11:10.640
I found him on the road.
He's barely clinging to life.

11:10.720 --> 11:12.080
Mrs. Zhao, help me get him inside.

11:12.840 --> 11:13.960
This…

11:14.040 --> 11:16.320
You don't even know who he is,
and you're hauling him home?

11:17.000 --> 11:17.920
And he's a full-grown man!

11:18.000 --> 11:19.880
You're an unmarried girl.

11:19.960 --> 11:21.560
Do you want to be the talk of the town?

11:22.760 --> 11:23.920
No one saw you, did they?

11:24.600 --> 11:27.840
His wounds look just like my parents'.

11:27.920 --> 11:29.040
He must've run into bandits too.

11:31.600 --> 11:32.600
There's no time to think about that.

11:34.280 --> 11:35.200
Help me carry him home.

11:35.960 --> 11:37.400
I can't bring trouble to your house.

11:37.480 --> 11:38.880
If he dies…

11:40.200 --> 11:42.640
Better he dies under a roof
than out in the snow.

11:44.120 --> 11:45.000
Come on.

11:49.080 --> 11:51.000
Mr. Zhao went to the post station
at the town gate.

11:51.600 --> 11:53.320
I'll get him back. You watch this man.

11:54.000 --> 11:54.920
Ning, come here.

11:55.840 --> 11:56.840
You stay too.

11:56.920 --> 11:59.200
A lone man and woman cannot share a room.

12:00.480 --> 12:01.600
I'll be back quickly.

12:01.680 --> 12:02.520
All right.

12:26.280 --> 12:27.320
He has bled so much.

12:29.160 --> 12:30.680
Before Mr. Zhao gets back,

12:30.760 --> 12:32.480
you must not die.

12:34.040 --> 12:35.880
I've followed Mr. Zhao
on house calls before.

12:38.600 --> 12:40.000
It's a long shot, but we have to try.

12:40.600 --> 12:42.280
Ning, go get a bowl of hot water.

12:42.360 --> 12:45.080
Mrs. Zhao said a lone man and woman
can't be alone together.

12:45.160 --> 12:46.160
I have to stay.

12:46.240 --> 12:47.320
Lone man and woman?

12:47.400 --> 12:48.400
He's halfway to becoming a ghost!

12:48.480 --> 12:49.600
Go.

13:02.240 --> 13:04.080
We used this much last time.

13:04.920 --> 13:06.880
But he's bleeding far worse…

13:09.600 --> 13:10.440
I'll use it all.

13:23.480 --> 13:24.880
What's going on, Changyu?

13:25.480 --> 13:26.320
He…

13:30.160 --> 13:31.320
Stop!

13:32.680 --> 13:34.760
-What are you doing?
-Giving him the medicine.

13:35.680 --> 13:37.720
You… Heavens above!

13:37.800 --> 13:39.960
That packet was one dose!
You poured the whole thing in?

13:40.040 --> 13:42.520
Are you trying to save him
or send him off?

13:42.600 --> 13:44.680
What were you thinking, Changyu?

13:46.280 --> 13:47.400
Last time

13:47.480 --> 13:49.000
there wasn't this much blood,

13:49.080 --> 13:50.560
so I added more.

13:52.200 --> 13:54.640
Last time it was a donkey. A donkey!

13:54.720 --> 13:56.560
You think man and beast are the same?

13:57.560 --> 13:59.160
With that much in one bowl,

13:59.240 --> 14:00.160
forget a man,

14:00.240 --> 14:02.960
even a braying mule would drop dead!

14:03.880 --> 14:05.360
Why are you shouting?

14:06.480 --> 14:08.560
I just wanted to save him.

14:08.640 --> 14:10.400
I didn't want him dying in your house,

14:11.000 --> 14:12.880
so I added more medicine.

14:12.960 --> 14:15.320
Even food can kill if you overdo it.
Why not just keep eating then?

14:15.920 --> 14:17.200
You can die from overeating?

14:18.560 --> 14:20.920
Enough. Both of you, out.

14:21.000 --> 14:22.760
Girls shouldn't be in here.

14:31.040 --> 14:33.760
Changyu can hardly put food on the table,

14:33.840 --> 14:35.440
and now she's dragging a stranger home.

14:35.520 --> 14:37.680
Why didn't you stop her?

14:37.760 --> 14:38.720
There.

14:38.800 --> 14:40.760
Look at that face. That's why.

14:40.840 --> 14:41.720
What was I supposed to do?

14:41.800 --> 14:43.840
What good is a handsome face?

14:43.920 --> 14:45.160
It won't keep you fed.

14:59.240 --> 15:01.440
This gentleman is really handsome.

15:01.520 --> 15:04.040
Is that why you carried him back, Changyu?

15:04.680 --> 15:05.720
Don't talk nonsense.

15:05.800 --> 15:06.880
A life is a life.

15:07.680 --> 15:08.880
His looks don't matter.

15:43.520 --> 15:46.280
The scouts tracked him
from Chongzhou to here.

15:46.360 --> 15:48.120
The blood trail ends at this spot.

15:48.720 --> 15:51.240
It snowed for a day and night.
The footprints are gone.

15:52.600 --> 15:54.120
This is Jizhou.

15:54.200 --> 15:55.680
He Jingyuan's territory.

15:55.760 --> 15:56.600
WEI SHENG

15:56.680 --> 15:58.280
We cannot search without leave.

15:58.360 --> 16:00.760
Report back to the capital.
Let the Chancellor decide.

16:00.840 --> 16:01.920
-Withdraw.
-Yes.

16:02.000 --> 16:02.920
Yes.

16:11.480 --> 16:12.840
SPRING BREEZE TOFU SHOP

16:23.600 --> 16:29.600
XIGU ALLEY

16:30.360 --> 16:31.480
You're back. Changyu.

16:32.200 --> 16:33.040
Changyu.

16:35.800 --> 16:36.960
Changyu.

16:37.040 --> 16:38.240
Changyu, wait!

16:42.840 --> 16:43.920
Changyu.

16:46.360 --> 16:47.760
Half a month apart,

16:47.840 --> 16:50.680
and you've grown even fairer.

16:52.400 --> 16:57.120
Is… Is this the medicine
you bought for Ning?

16:57.200 --> 16:58.280
I've got something--

16:58.360 --> 17:00.040
If you have something to say,
say it plainly.

17:01.240 --> 17:03.040
I was thinking…

17:03.120 --> 17:04.599
Since the engagement

17:04.680 --> 17:06.480
between our families is already dissolved,

17:06.560 --> 17:08.720
that betrothal letter
is useless to you now.

17:09.520 --> 17:11.119
-So perhaps--
-You want it back?

17:12.720 --> 17:13.680
Fine.

17:14.240 --> 17:15.280
Settle the accounts first.

17:15.880 --> 17:18.400
All those years
I covered Song Yan's tuition.

17:19.119 --> 17:21.000
All the help my family
gave you and your mother.

17:21.520 --> 17:23.720
Clear the debt.
Then you can have your letter.

17:24.560 --> 17:27.319
You can't blame us for breaking it off.

17:27.400 --> 17:29.960
The fortune teller said
your birth chart is ill-omened.

17:30.040 --> 17:31.440
Should my son marry a wife

17:31.520 --> 17:33.400
fated to bring harm to her husband?

17:34.120 --> 17:35.560
If we speak of debts,

17:35.640 --> 17:37.480
what we owe was to your parents,

17:37.560 --> 17:38.800
not to you.

17:39.480 --> 17:41.200
The betrothal letter
was signed by my father.

17:41.280 --> 17:42.560
If you want it, go ask him for it.

17:43.880 --> 17:44.880
You insolent girl!

17:45.520 --> 17:47.320
-Stand still!
-Mother.

17:54.080 --> 17:54.920
Calm yourself.

17:56.120 --> 17:56.960
Some things

17:59.640 --> 18:01.840
should be said by me.

18:03.760 --> 18:05.200
Yan,

18:05.280 --> 18:06.520
this shameless girl

18:06.600 --> 18:09.040
has her eye on your future title.

18:09.120 --> 18:11.680
She knows you're soft-hearted.

18:11.760 --> 18:13.360
That's why she won't let go.

18:13.440 --> 18:16.440
She's here to hold past kindness over you!

18:18.240 --> 18:19.880
-In a few days, the magistrate
-Holding kindness…

18:19.960 --> 18:21.120
will send for us to move.

18:21.200 --> 18:22.160
-…over him?
-She won't have the nerve

18:22.240 --> 18:23.800
-to show her face again!
-Mother, please go inside.

18:33.480 --> 18:34.600
Changyu.

18:34.680 --> 18:36.800
I am not an ungrateful man.

18:38.160 --> 18:39.960
I always remember your family's kindness.

18:40.880 --> 18:42.480
But of all virtues,
filial piety comes first.

18:42.560 --> 18:44.480
If I defy my mother
and force this marriage,

18:44.560 --> 18:46.160
I become unfilial.

18:48.120 --> 18:50.480
Even if we can't be husband and wife,
we can still be family.

18:51.160 --> 18:53.000
As for your words just now,

18:53.080 --> 18:55.120
I will take them as anger.
I won't hold them against you.

18:55.200 --> 18:56.200
No.

18:57.000 --> 18:58.720
You must hold them against me.

18:59.320 --> 19:01.240
And spare me the family talk.

19:02.000 --> 19:03.720
Even friends settle their debts.

19:04.440 --> 19:05.920
What I despise most

19:06.640 --> 19:08.680
is people wagging their tongues
behind my back.

19:09.600 --> 19:11.800
Calling me a jinx.

19:11.880 --> 19:13.800
Saying I'm holding
past kindness over them.

19:13.880 --> 19:16.320
Claiming I'm forcing Song Yan to marry me!

19:16.400 --> 19:18.920
That's what others say.
What does that have to do with me?

19:19.000 --> 19:20.520
I never said it was you.

19:20.600 --> 19:21.960
Why are you so eager to claim it?

19:22.880 --> 19:24.120
-You wretched girl--
-Mother.

19:24.200 --> 19:25.120
Changyu.

19:25.200 --> 19:26.520
I do not care what others think.

19:26.600 --> 19:28.280
Do all those years of feelings

19:28.920 --> 19:30.560
mean so little,
you'd weigh them against gold?

19:30.640 --> 19:32.480
Yes. That is exactly how they are weighed.

19:34.080 --> 19:36.760
You hand over the money.
I return the betrothal letter.

19:37.320 --> 19:39.200
Do not sicken me with talk of feelings.

19:40.000 --> 19:41.800
I'd rather raise pigs than deal

19:41.880 --> 19:42.920
with the likes of you.

19:44.880 --> 19:46.520
You're nothing but ungrateful snakes.

19:47.200 --> 19:48.520
What did you say?

19:49.240 --> 19:51.960
What did you say? Watch your mouth!

19:52.040 --> 19:53.160
-You're the pig!
-Mother.

19:53.240 --> 19:54.440
Your whole family are pigs!

19:54.520 --> 19:56.240
-Mother.
-No wonder you're a butcher!

19:56.800 --> 19:58.160
Unbelievable.

19:59.760 --> 20:01.120
Guess the old saying's right,

20:01.880 --> 20:04.360
"Never waste your money on a man."

20:04.920 --> 20:07.200
There's still a man lying in your room.

20:08.920 --> 20:10.160
You nearly scared me to death.

20:13.040 --> 20:13.960
Here.

20:14.520 --> 20:16.840
That's quite a pile
of that never-spend-on-a-man money.

20:20.120 --> 20:21.640
Changyu.

20:21.720 --> 20:24.440
That young fellow's awake. Go take a look.

20:25.040 --> 20:25.880
Really?

20:27.120 --> 20:28.960
I thought he was as good as gone.

20:29.040 --> 20:30.520
Mr. Zhao, you work miracles.

20:30.600 --> 20:32.320
Beast or man, you treat them all the same.

20:36.560 --> 20:38.600
Is that praise or an insult?

20:47.000 --> 20:47.960
You're awake.

21:15.840 --> 21:17.080
I…

21:17.160 --> 21:18.320
I saw you collapsed in the snow.

21:19.040 --> 21:20.640
That's why I carried you back.

21:21.240 --> 21:23.800
But the one who saved your life
was Mr. Zhao.

21:26.920 --> 21:28.640
He even changed your clothes.

21:31.840 --> 21:32.880
This is his home.

21:34.760 --> 21:36.120
He's a physician.

21:36.200 --> 21:37.640
Usually treats mules and horses.

21:39.480 --> 21:40.960
He treats people too.

21:47.200 --> 21:48.160
My thanks.

21:50.400 --> 21:51.920
When you carried me back,

21:53.040 --> 21:54.680
did you see anyone else?

21:54.760 --> 21:55.880
Anyone else?

21:57.520 --> 21:58.520
You were the only one there.

21:58.600 --> 22:00.760
Were there others buried in the snow?

22:17.880 --> 22:19.000
I'll fetch you some water.

22:20.880 --> 22:21.720
Here.

22:25.160 --> 22:26.760
Where am I?

22:29.280 --> 22:31.720
Xigu Alley in Lin'an Town,
Qingping County.

22:32.960 --> 22:35.080
You don't look like
you're from around here.

22:35.160 --> 22:37.240
Where are you from? What's your name?

22:37.320 --> 22:38.800
Did you run into bandits?

22:44.160 --> 22:45.200
My name is Yan Zheng.

22:46.600 --> 22:47.760
Yan as in speech.

22:48.440 --> 22:49.440
Zheng as in righteousness.

22:50.600 --> 22:53.440
I fled here from Chongzhou.

22:57.240 --> 22:58.720
Do you have family left?

23:21.760 --> 23:22.800
I'm the last of my name.

23:24.440 --> 23:25.440
The last of your name?

23:26.960 --> 23:29.840
So your family has a different last name?
You've got a stepfather?

23:34.520 --> 23:35.960
No.

23:36.040 --> 23:37.440
I mean there's only me.

23:40.720 --> 23:41.800
I'm sorry.

23:42.680 --> 23:44.360
No wonder when we found you,

23:45.120 --> 23:46.640
you kept calling for your mother.

24:02.280 --> 24:04.440
-Mr. Zhao!
-What's wrong?

24:04.520 --> 24:05.840
Why's he coughing like that?

24:06.520 --> 24:08.120
I only mentioned his mother,

24:08.200 --> 24:09.400
then he started coughing.

24:09.480 --> 24:11.280
Why would you bring up his mother now?

24:11.360 --> 24:15.000
You can't agitate the sick, Mother of God.

24:15.080 --> 24:16.520
And you still said it.

24:19.640 --> 24:22.240
-See?
-Quick, help him lie back down.

24:25.640 --> 24:29.360
Yan Zheng. Yan Zheng…

24:30.360 --> 24:32.240
‎YAN

24:32.320 --> 24:35.560
If I asked one question too many
and he dies because of it, what then?

24:36.720 --> 24:38.520
Even a cheap coffin costs silver.

24:40.240 --> 24:41.120
Or

24:41.800 --> 24:43.440
we could dig a pit and bury him.

24:43.520 --> 24:44.720
Changyu,

24:44.800 --> 24:47.160
should we ask Heaven?

24:48.800 --> 24:49.640
All right.

24:50.440 --> 24:51.520
Let Heaven decide.

24:52.600 --> 24:53.440
We'll pull grass.

24:56.720 --> 24:59.080
If mine snaps, we buy a coffin.

24:59.160 --> 25:00.680
If yours snaps, we dig a pit.

25:00.760 --> 25:01.680
Deal.

25:06.880 --> 25:07.720
Best of three.

25:11.360 --> 25:13.200
Nothing beyond three. Again.

25:16.440 --> 25:18.120
Heaven's answered three times.

25:18.200 --> 25:19.320
Buy the coffin.

25:19.400 --> 25:21.360
My purse has spoken once.

25:23.360 --> 25:24.200
Dig the pit.

25:35.120 --> 25:36.320
Mr. Zhao.

25:36.400 --> 25:37.640
If he doesn't pull through,
don't blame yourself.

25:38.480 --> 25:39.680
It's fate.

25:42.800 --> 25:43.680
What's this?

25:45.080 --> 25:46.600
Changyu's stingy.

25:46.680 --> 25:50.080
Heaven told her to buy
the handsome gentleman a coffin,

25:50.160 --> 25:51.920
but she insists on digging a hole instead.

25:52.000 --> 25:53.560
Who's being stingy?

25:53.640 --> 25:54.880
I even wrote him a memorial tablet.

25:54.960 --> 25:56.240
See? Yan Zheng.

25:57.240 --> 25:59.240
Good thing I know
how to write both characters.

26:02.520 --> 26:04.840
Get that unlucky thing out of here!

26:04.920 --> 26:06.920
That young man has a strong constitution.

26:08.040 --> 26:08.960
And last night,

26:09.040 --> 26:11.200
you gave him hemostatic decoction.

26:11.280 --> 26:12.640
He coughed up some clotted blood.

26:12.720 --> 26:14.600
That saved him.

26:14.680 --> 26:16.400
That's wonderful!

26:16.480 --> 26:17.360
He's alive!

26:17.440 --> 26:19.720
He's alive, he's alive!

26:19.800 --> 26:21.520
Don't celebrate just yet.

26:21.600 --> 26:23.280
The medicine he'll need from now on

26:23.360 --> 26:24.840
will cost more than coffin boards.

26:25.960 --> 26:27.080
Ning.

26:27.880 --> 26:29.880
We're having noodles tonight.
Go to the kitchen

26:29.960 --> 26:31.560
and bring me
half a basin of braising stock.

26:31.640 --> 26:32.480
All right.

26:35.680 --> 26:37.240
Changyu, come here.

26:40.480 --> 26:42.120
What were you thinking?

26:43.680 --> 26:45.360
Ning's been frail her whole life.

26:45.440 --> 26:46.480
She's still taking medicine herself.

26:46.560 --> 26:48.080
Where will you get the money to treat him?

26:48.960 --> 26:50.280
Does that young man

26:50.360 --> 26:52.080
have any kin left?

26:52.760 --> 26:54.160
He's the last of his name.

26:55.560 --> 26:56.920
-He's what?
-He's what?

26:58.520 --> 27:00.160
He says his family's gone.

27:00.240 --> 27:01.720
He's the only one left.

27:01.800 --> 27:03.240
He fled from Chongzhou.

27:03.840 --> 27:06.000
Then he met bandits near Hucha Pass.

27:06.520 --> 27:07.480
Right now,

27:08.400 --> 27:09.600
he likely has nowhere to go.

27:10.600 --> 27:11.840
Did he have

27:11.920 --> 27:13.360
any silver on him?

27:13.440 --> 27:14.440
Travel papers?

27:15.040 --> 27:16.040
When I changed his clothes,

27:16.120 --> 27:17.840
I searched him clean. Not a single coin.

27:18.400 --> 27:21.160
Either the bandits took everything

27:21.240 --> 27:23.280
or he's poorer than I am.

27:27.360 --> 27:29.360
Why not carry him to the county yamen?

27:29.440 --> 27:31.080
Let the officials decide.

27:31.680 --> 27:32.520
That won't work.

27:32.600 --> 27:34.200
How many beggars lie outside that gate?

27:34.280 --> 27:36.360
-Have you ever seen them lift a finger?
-True.

27:37.120 --> 27:39.320
If he were dead, we could
dispose of him however we liked.

27:39.400 --> 27:41.240
But he's breathing.
We can't pretend we don't see it.

27:44.920 --> 27:49.040
Let him recover first.
I'll find a way for the money.

27:56.920 --> 27:59.640
XIGU ALLEY

27:59.720 --> 28:02.240
The air is dry.

28:03.240 --> 28:05.640
Beware of fire.

28:05.720 --> 28:10.760
HAVE A FULL MEAL

28:21.480 --> 28:24.520
Two, four, six, eight, ten…

28:27.440 --> 28:29.760
Five… ten… eleven…

28:50.840 --> 28:54.280
Mother, if it was truly you
who led me to save him,

28:55.120 --> 28:57.240
should I see it through?

29:03.800 --> 29:05.160
What am I to do?

29:45.040 --> 29:48.360
‎LIN'AN, SUN'S BAMBOO WORKSHOP

29:48.440 --> 29:50.000
LUO'S PAWNSHOP

29:50.080 --> 29:51.000
One tael?

29:51.760 --> 29:53.560
This hairpin is solid silver!

29:53.640 --> 29:55.160
My father paid three or four taels for it.

29:55.240 --> 29:57.720
It is silver.

29:57.800 --> 30:00.640
I can give you one tael and five mace.

30:00.720 --> 30:02.800
If your family
hadn't fallen on hard times,

30:02.880 --> 30:05.000
and if you went elsewhere…

30:05.080 --> 30:07.520
Wait, wait! Don't leave.

30:07.600 --> 30:09.440
We can discuss it.

30:13.560 --> 30:15.840
Two taels. Not a coin less.

30:17.880 --> 30:18.840
Fine, fine.

30:19.520 --> 30:22.160
For the sake
of being neighbors in Xigu Alley,

30:22.240 --> 30:23.600
let's call it a good deed.

30:24.840 --> 30:25.720
Press your thumbprint.

30:27.280 --> 30:28.640
I will redeem it.

30:29.320 --> 30:30.720
It means a great deal to me.

30:30.800 --> 30:32.040
Rest easy.

30:38.080 --> 30:39.680
‎PAWN VALUE: TWO TAELS OF PURE SILVER
‎SIGNED AND SEALED

30:39.760 --> 30:41.800
‎SIXTEENTH DAY OF THE TWELFTH MONTH,
‎SIXTEENTH YEAR OF ZHENGPING

30:49.360 --> 30:50.960
What a rare little treasure.

30:54.960 --> 30:55.960
Move along.

30:56.040 --> 30:57.040
Changyu.

30:57.600 --> 30:58.480
Bought new pigs?

30:59.000 --> 31:01.120
Fan's Pork Stall reopens tomorrow.

31:01.800 --> 31:03.480
Everyone, come show your support!

31:03.560 --> 31:04.640
Look who's in charge now.

31:04.720 --> 31:05.720
We'll be there.

31:07.000 --> 31:07.840
Changyu.

31:09.600 --> 31:10.600
Mr. Li.

31:10.680 --> 31:12.920
So you're carrying on your father's trade?

31:13.560 --> 31:15.440
A girl's gotta eat.

31:15.520 --> 31:16.440
That's right.

31:16.520 --> 31:19.000
Don't mind what people say
about slaughtering pigs.

31:19.080 --> 31:20.240
Hunger knows no gender,

31:20.320 --> 31:21.800
and neither should work.

31:22.400 --> 31:23.920
Thank you, Mr. Li. Look here.

31:24.000 --> 31:26.200
I picked this one
using the method my father taught me.

31:26.960 --> 31:29.200
See those round haunches?
Short, thick tail.

31:29.280 --> 31:31.120
That means thick hide and good fat.

31:31.200 --> 31:32.840
The meat will be top quality.

31:32.920 --> 31:34.040
If it's that good,

31:34.120 --> 31:35.400
of course, we'll snatch it up.

31:35.480 --> 31:37.200
Yixiang Restaurant reserves
half a carcass.

31:37.280 --> 31:38.280
Thank you, Mr. Li.

31:38.360 --> 31:39.640
-I'll be off then.
-All right.

31:40.400 --> 31:41.760
Come on. Move along.

31:43.960 --> 31:45.040
Sooie! Sooie!

31:45.120 --> 31:46.360
Sooie! Sooie!

31:46.440 --> 31:47.920
-Sooie! Sooie!
-Changyu.

31:48.000 --> 31:49.320
-Got the pigs back?
-Yes.

31:49.400 --> 31:50.320
That's a fine, fat one.

31:51.520 --> 31:52.560
Sooie! Sooie!

31:52.640 --> 31:53.480
Sooie…

32:01.680 --> 32:02.600
Good pig.

32:03.680 --> 32:05.720
Don't block the road. Keep moving.

32:11.680 --> 32:13.240
Move. Get on.

32:13.320 --> 32:14.840
Go on. Come on.

32:16.560 --> 32:17.400
There.

32:18.160 --> 32:19.080
Sooie! Sooie!

32:19.880 --> 32:20.720
Home!

33:02.760 --> 33:06.840
ARE YOU UNHARMED? REPLY AT ONCE

33:39.400 --> 33:41.360
XIGU ALLEY, LIN'AN TOWN, QINGPING COUNTY

34:25.320 --> 34:27.120
A white hawk?

34:44.120 --> 34:45.600
Who threw that?

34:45.679 --> 34:46.679
That hurt!

34:54.880 --> 34:56.040
Where did this stone come from?

34:57.520 --> 34:58.960
Which scoundrel threw that at me?

35:00.000 --> 35:01.560
I'll break their legs!

35:01.640 --> 35:02.480
Move.

35:04.200 --> 35:05.520
Are you sure you haven't seen him?

35:05.600 --> 35:06.880
No, sir. I'm from this village.

35:06.960 --> 35:07.960
Anyone harboring displaced refugees

35:08.040 --> 35:09.040
will be imprisoned.

35:09.120 --> 35:10.720
-Report truthfully. Search that side.
-Certainly, sir.

35:15.720 --> 35:16.680
-What's happened?
-Enough chatter.

35:16.760 --> 35:17.600
How many households here?

35:18.240 --> 35:21.640
Sir, perhaps you should
see a doctor first--

35:21.720 --> 35:23.600
Like hell I will!
You men, check those houses.

35:23.680 --> 35:24.520
-Yes, sir.
-Yes, sir.

35:31.560 --> 35:32.440
‎Come on.

35:32.520 --> 35:34.440
Excuse me. What's going on?

35:34.520 --> 35:35.880
They're searching house to house

35:35.960 --> 35:37.760
for refugees without registration.

35:40.480 --> 35:41.560
That gave me a fright.

35:41.640 --> 35:42.760
I thought it was tax collectors.

35:45.360 --> 35:46.920
Why search for refugees all of a sudden?

35:47.000 --> 35:48.520
They're rounding them up

35:48.600 --> 35:50.160
and sending them to the Chongzhou front.

35:50.240 --> 35:51.800
The fighting's urgent.

35:51.880 --> 35:53.960
Once you're sent, you're thrown
straight into the vanguard.

35:54.720 --> 35:56.680
What's the vanguard? Is that elite?

35:57.400 --> 35:58.400
It's where they send you to die.

36:16.800 --> 36:17.880
Yan Zheng.

36:17.960 --> 36:19.840
Do you have travel papers
and registration documents?

36:24.200 --> 36:25.320
I did.

36:26.480 --> 36:27.400
They're gone.

36:28.800 --> 36:29.640
Gone?

36:31.000 --> 36:32.080
Search again.

36:32.600 --> 36:34.000
Were they on you?

36:34.080 --> 36:35.280
When you changed my clothes,

36:35.360 --> 36:37.160
didn't you search me thoroughly?

36:37.240 --> 36:38.200
I…

36:41.520 --> 36:43.360
I only did that to save your life.

36:43.440 --> 36:44.720
Don't get the wrong idea.

36:46.360 --> 36:47.200
How did you know?

36:48.120 --> 36:49.120
You…

36:50.720 --> 36:52.280
This isn't the time for that.

36:52.360 --> 36:53.760
Without travel papers,

36:53.840 --> 36:55.160
they'll treat you as a refugee.

36:55.240 --> 36:56.640
They'll drag you to the vanguard.

37:02.400 --> 37:03.520
What do we do?

37:03.600 --> 37:04.760
The soldiers are almost here.

37:05.560 --> 37:06.800
Since they're here,

37:07.960 --> 37:09.600
I cannot stay.

37:09.680 --> 37:11.120
I won't bring trouble upon you.

37:22.560 --> 37:23.400
I have an idea.

37:25.040 --> 37:26.360
There's somewhere you can hide.

37:28.320 --> 37:29.160
Open up!

37:30.200 --> 37:31.040
Open the door!

37:31.960 --> 37:32.800
Open up!

37:38.360 --> 37:39.880
Village head. What's happening?

37:43.280 --> 37:44.480
Changyu.

37:44.560 --> 37:45.840
Is it just you at home?

37:47.960 --> 37:49.760
Sir, this is the Fan house.

37:50.800 --> 37:53.200
It connects to the Zhao house next door.

37:55.320 --> 37:57.240
Is there a stranger staying here?

37:58.000 --> 37:58.840
No, sir.

37:59.400 --> 38:00.960
We're a small place.

38:01.040 --> 38:03.120
Everyone knows everyone.

38:03.840 --> 38:06.400
We'd notice even a stray dog.
There's no one.

38:09.280 --> 38:10.120
Clear.

38:11.960 --> 38:13.200
-Clear.
-Clear.

38:14.080 --> 38:14.920
Clear.

38:20.680 --> 38:21.840
Captain!

38:25.040 --> 38:25.880
Captain, look at this.

38:28.240 --> 38:29.720
A bloodstained cloth.

38:30.240 --> 38:31.280
Explain yourself.

38:32.040 --> 38:32.920
Explain!

38:34.360 --> 38:35.960
Who in this house is injured?

38:36.040 --> 38:37.280
No one.

38:38.320 --> 38:39.200
I slaughter pigs.

38:39.800 --> 38:40.960
That's a knife rag.

38:41.480 --> 38:43.480
I butchered a pig a few days ago.

38:44.560 --> 38:45.760
A knife rag?

38:47.400 --> 38:49.000
You two guard the front yard.

38:49.080 --> 38:50.640
The rest, with me.

38:57.200 --> 38:58.120
Sir,

38:58.200 --> 39:01.120
the Fan family has always been butchers.

39:03.360 --> 39:04.480
You're just a young woman.

39:05.080 --> 39:06.480
You can slaughter a pig alone?

39:09.040 --> 39:12.120
Do you understand
that hiding refugees is a grave crime?

39:12.200 --> 39:13.720
It is treated as aiding the enemy.

39:13.800 --> 39:15.200
The entire household can be exiled.

39:15.280 --> 39:16.680
Sent to serve in the army.

39:17.600 --> 39:18.440
Sir.

39:19.360 --> 39:20.880
My parents are already gone.

39:22.120 --> 39:23.320
Our whole family

39:23.400 --> 39:24.720
is just my little sister and me.

39:27.160 --> 39:29.640
Changyu, come here.

39:30.720 --> 39:33.000
Did you truly have someone hidden?

39:34.040 --> 39:35.680
If one household harbors a refugee,

39:35.760 --> 39:37.200
ten households bear the punishment.

39:37.960 --> 39:39.760
You wouldn't want the neighbors

39:39.840 --> 39:41.680
to suffer because of you.

39:42.720 --> 39:44.880
Hand him over now.

39:44.960 --> 39:46.920
I can still speak for you.

39:47.760 --> 39:50.680
Say you were forced.

40:04.800 --> 40:06.040
Stand ready!

40:19.040 --> 40:20.320
They've found you!

40:22.040 --> 40:22.880
Come here.

40:25.080 --> 40:26.640
Forgive us, sir.

40:26.720 --> 40:28.360
We were playing hide-and-seek.

40:28.440 --> 40:30.240
You arrived so suddenly,

40:30.320 --> 40:31.920
I didn't have time to call her out.

40:36.720 --> 40:38.800
-Clear.
-Clear.

40:41.680 --> 40:42.560
That's enough.

40:42.640 --> 40:44.200
Check the next house. Move.

40:46.920 --> 40:48.800
FAN

40:50.960 --> 40:52.760
You. Search the pigsty too.

40:53.720 --> 40:54.640
Yes, sir.

40:57.920 --> 40:59.400
Always making me search.

41:01.240 --> 41:03.200
A filthy pigpen. What's there to find?

41:23.160 --> 41:24.640
Sir, mind the pigs. They bite.

41:34.160 --> 41:36.080
Sir, watch your step! There's offal.

41:41.800 --> 41:42.960
No one here!

41:43.040 --> 41:44.560
Just two pigs.

41:50.840 --> 41:52.640
Ning, lock the courtyard gate.

42:00.680 --> 42:01.600
It's me.

42:09.360 --> 42:10.200
I'm back.

42:25.640 --> 42:26.960
They've all gone.

42:28.960 --> 42:29.960
Don't worry.

43:00.080 --> 43:00.920
It's over.

43:17.200 --> 43:21.040
END CREDIT SCENE

43:23.240 --> 43:24.720
Bravo!

43:31.680 --> 43:38.400
XIANGTENG TROUPE

43:47.160 --> 43:48.600
Whose child is this? Get out!

43:49.240 --> 43:50.120
Out!

43:52.480 --> 43:55.000
Don't come near here. Whose child is this?

43:55.080 --> 43:57.600
Don't run!

44:01.040 --> 44:01.880
That rascal.

44:03.040 --> 44:04.160
Everyone, forgive us.

44:04.240 --> 44:05.080
Our apologies.

46:49.080 --> 46:52.600
‎NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
‎IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:52.680 --> 46:53.560
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
